                            <comment id="12604039" author="doronc" created="Tue, 10 Jun 2008 22:00:51 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch sets BTQ explanation as match according to score of non-payload part.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also in this patch: while at it I noticed that TestBTQ sets indexing time boost to 0 and hence one assertion on search results was commented out.&lt;br/&gt;
